</section><section id="text-7" class="widget widget--home widget_text"> <div class="textwidget"><p>A lot of domestic helpers are working in Hong Kong, Singapore or Dubai and it&#8217;s sometimes challenging for them to get a new job. HelperPlace is a facilitating platform which connect helpers and maids to a new employer. <strong>Is it time for you to search a new employer?</strong></p>
</div>
