<div class="testimonials component effect-fade">
<div class="testimonials-list">
<blockquote id="quote-1759" class="woothemes-testimonial woothemes-testimonial--individual"><p>HelperPlace allows me to connect with more than 10 drivers. 1 week later, I recruited one of them .</p>
<cite class="woothemes-testimonial--individual__author"><img width="56" height="70" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.helperplace.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/David-looking-Driver.png?fit=56%2C70&amp;ssl=1" class="avatar wp-post-image" alt="Connect with 10 drivers" data-attachment-id="99991672" data-permalink="https://www.helperplace.com/david-looking-driver" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.helperplace.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/David-looking-Driver.png?fit=200%2C248&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="200,248" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="David-looking-Driver" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.helperplace.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/David-looking-Driver.png?fit=200%2C248&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.helperplace.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/David-looking-Driver.png?fit=200%2C248&amp;ssl=1" /> <cite class="author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">David P.</span></cite>
